{"word":"G4912 - συνέχω - synéchō - soon-ekh'-o - Constrain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synéchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Constrain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடக்கிட, அடைத்துக்கொள், வருத்தப்பட்டுக்கிட"},{"paragraph":"1. to hold together"},{"paragraph":"2. to hold together with constraint, to compress"},{"paragraph":"3. to hold completely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold together</i>, that is, to <i>compress</i> (the ears, with a crowd or siege) or <i>arrest</i> (a prisoner); figuratively to <i>compel</i>, <i>perplex</i>, <i>afflict</i>, <i>preoccupy:</i> - constrain, hold, keep in, press, lie sick of, stop, be in a strait, straiten, be taken with, throng.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4912/4912\">G4912</a>, <a href=\"#/G4928/4928\">G4928</a>"}]}